</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 28 degrees C., max. 36 degrees C., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Sydney: min. 17 degrees C., max. 24 degrees C., heavy rain,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Karachi: min. 22 degrees C., max. 35 degrees, clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Cairo: min. 21 degrees C., max. 36 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Moscow: min. 3 degrees C., max. 8 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. 4 degrees C., max. 11 degrees C., overcast,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 2 degrees C., max. 8 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 2 degrees C., max. 7 degrees C., clear to drizzle,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
New York: min. 5 degrees C., max. 16 degrees C., cloudy to
clear, calm to gentle breeze.  
