Nimmanhaeminda will tell the international community that Thailand
is committed to reforms when he attends a meeting of finance
ministers in Washington next week.
</P>
<P>
Finance ministers from 22 countries will participate in the
meeting which will seek global cooperation in tackling the crisis
in the monetary market.
</P>
